        d
        
          T
          
            ∗
          
        
        μ
      
    
    {\displaystyle \int _{T(\Omega )}gd\mu =\int _{\Omega }g\circ TdT^{*}\mu }
  .
Pushforward measure and transformation formula
The pushforward measure in terms of a transformation 
  
    
      
        T
      
    
    {\displaystyle T}
  , is defined as 
  
    
      
        
