    {\displaystyle \int _{T(\Omega )}gd\mu =\int _{\Omega }g\circ TdT^{*}\mu =\int _{\Omega }g\circ T|{\text{det}}D_{x}T|dm(x)}
  
The change of variables formula for pushforward measure:
  
    
      
        
          ∫
          
            Ω
          
        
